data.description: Take a look at this Wall home with a pool.  It has 4 bedrooms and sits on three lots (1.2 acres).  There are huge trees that surround this great home.  The back yard had a huge deck and is ready for your backyard parties around the pool.  Inside you will find a large living area that has a great fireplace.  There is also a fireplace in the master bedroom.  One of the lots could be sold off our used to build another home in Wall School district.  Call to set up an appointment today.
